            <trans-unit id="tl_url_rewrite.conditionalResponseUri.1">
                <source>Just like for the request conditions, use Symfony's Expression Language (e.g. &lt;em&gt;request.getPreferredLanguage() starts with 'de'&lt;/em&gt;) as key and as the value, use dynamic redirect URLs. If no condition matches, the regular redirect URL acts as a fallback. This way you can e.g. forward differently depending on the browser language.</source>
